workflow_runs.name: Build RPCSX Core with NCE v8 JIT
workflow_runs.display_title: Fix: LLVM Turbo in decoder list + firmware persistence

head_commit.message:
Fix: LLVM Turbo in decoder list + firmware persistence

1. LLVM Turbo now appears as option in PPU/SPU Decoder dropdown
   - PPU Decoder: NCE, LLVM Turbo, LLVM 19, Interpreter
   - SPU Decoder: LLVM Turbo, ASMJIT, Interpreter

2. Fixed firmware disappearing after restart
   - Added FirmwareRepository.load() call on app startup
   - Firmware info now persists in fw.json

3. Removed separate Turbo switch buttons (integrated into dropdown)
